Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少上好鎖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是這麼說沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知道裕一何時會過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一  發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為不知道 才問你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  別一臉認真的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…什麼也沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們成為朋友時的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們初次見面的時候不就是朋友了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個不錯的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種季節打雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚會下雨的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有繩子之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小司  拿著繩子的這…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個假面算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被人發現我擅自進入醫院會很麻煩的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要爬過去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小司  拿著繩子的這頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本書  絕不可以被淋濕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好嗎  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔神 大風車固定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小司  還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一  快一點  手要滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世古口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戎崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然家裡不能養
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少能幫你一起求情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼有這麼高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,39度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再量一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  沖  快衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子  不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小司  多田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子  也以這種氣勢衝向她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  真可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香  總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你的手術結束精神恢復後  一起去遠方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  帶上便當去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去過海邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼由我帶你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像上次帶你去炮台山那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼幫我拿回了書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本書  是你父親給你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被淋濕的話  會很傷心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  里香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是打算那麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  因為我也撒了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使夏目大夫沒有說  我也打算和裕一和好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  就像是在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這就是在夢中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  里香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是古怪  剛才在人家的病房前幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個非常好吃耶  要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  拿來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要顯得這麼得意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有好好接到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的吧  因為距離這麼近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無趣  不可以說句「Nice  Catch」之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了你的病房  卻發現裕一發燒而昏睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下得那麼大還去撿  真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice Catch
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又為什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說  里香去過我的病房…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  並不是一場夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了  萌萌體育褲  非常可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了  未亡人旅情  非常色情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了  眼鏡娘熱潮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  多田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼  這些全部是A書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是別人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不賴  這就是傳說中的戎崎珍藏品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多田珍藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香叫我燒掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部燒掉的話  就原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個引起飯菜全扔事件的里香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣就原諒你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯菜全扔事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在以前的醫院  我的同事打攪到了里香的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你猜里香那傢伙做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是故意把一隻筆弄到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我的同事正打算拾起來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香把飯全部扣在了同事頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是把味噌汁澆上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的小菜都一個接一個地扔了上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  布丁倒是有留下  你能相信這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香的話真能做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同事完全敗給了她  向她的主治大夫哭訴不停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然叫那個里香原諒了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底用了什麼手段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:11:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喬邦尼用宛如吹著口哨般的寂寞口吻」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「從幽暗的排著扁柏的坡道走了下來」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  小帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼小帥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香在叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去轉告她裕一正忙著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嘛  你用不著客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正都是閒著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞希子小姐  你會吹口哨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口哨？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彪摩托車時用來做暗號的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要U字型轉彎啦」之類「給我超」之類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「全給我幹掉」之類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得要對里香溫柔一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在正常範圍內  逐漸增加行走的距離吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  把嘴巴張開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在還冷  散步時注意不要著涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一  你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得畏畏縮縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行嗎  休息一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不用擔心的  喬邦尼」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是嗎  康帕蕾拉」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我已經完完全全到達天原了」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是「銀河鐵道」裡的台詞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真記得住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都讀了好幾回了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  到達天原了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夫  請注意不要在這裡吸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是香煙型巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  請不要吸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說這是香煙型巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久侯多時了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過一兩個月就要到春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等暖和了  就從病院溜出去一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到附近的河邊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡還有櫻花道 可漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去我想去 帶我去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「母親會原諒我嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我只要能讓母親幸福  什麼事都會做」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但什麼事才能使母親最幸福呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你的母親並不會奢求太多吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我不知道  但無論是誰…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果真的做了好事  是最幸福的呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「所以我覺得母親會原諒我的」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真記得住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「康帕蕾拉好像下了個什麼決心一樣」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「馬上就到白鳥車站了呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「十一點整應該可以到了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戎崎你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  要偷跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿精神也是好事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒了嗎  大夫你是在值班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微喝一點酒也不會醉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒酒  陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戎崎  你也喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你是未成年人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肝炎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你很快樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一臉快樂的不得了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為里香是個美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17歲吧  最棒的年齡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那麼可愛的女孩一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣就開心死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經也是這樣  所以很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但別癡心妄想了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情很快就會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是一個成人  還妒嫉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  你看不慣我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直呆在里香的身邊  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…根本不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說我明白的嗎  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能這樣樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能這樣傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:19:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能所有的事情都能一帆風順
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭一哭病就會好了嗎  笑一笑就會好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望不過是如同垃圾一樣的東西  你卻還一直糾纏著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在…就在你考資格認證  寫論文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著今後的去向的同時…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「康帕蕾拉  又變成我倆獨處了呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「無論何處  我們也一起去」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我已經如同那蠍子一樣 」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果真的是為了大家的幸福的話」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我的身體即使被火燒一百次也無所謂」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嗯  我也是一樣」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「然而  真正的幸福究竟是什麼呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我不知道」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「說什麼啊  振作一點」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊 那裡是黑洞哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「宇宙的大洞」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我就算處於那樣巨大的黑暗中也不會害怕」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一定要去找尋大家真正的幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「無論是何處  我們也一同前往」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  里香  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小孩子掉落在水中」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喬邦尼  康帕蕾拉急忙趕往河川」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「已經沒救了  已經落水45分鐘了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不用擔心的  喬邦尼」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能這樣樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能一切都會一帆風順
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓣膜的組織非常脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  輪廓和以前相比模糊多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是周圍的組織持續肥大的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣繼續下去  也不見得會有好轉
